<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.3.6">
<l>maiyoṇ karuṅkaṭalum nilaṉuma ṇivaraiyum</l>
<l>ceyya cuṭariraṇṭu mivaiyāya niṉṉaineñcil</l>
<l>uyyum vakaiyuṇarntē ṇuṇmaiyāli ṉiyātumaṟṟōr</l>
<l>teyvam piṟitaṟiyēṉ tiruviṇṇa karāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You, who became these: the dark sea, as bright as ink, the land,</l>
<l>Beautiful mountains, and the two perfect orbs,</l>
<l>I truly realized in my heart as the way which [I] will be saved;</l>
<l>Since [then], moreover, I do not know of any other god,</l>
<l rend="indent">[Lord] of Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
